        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-3">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="mb-3"> <div class="card-nino shadow-sm"> <div class="card-body text-center"> <strong>About Us</strong> </div> </div> </div>
                    <p>We understand the impact that your oral health can have on the well-being of your entire body. Diseases of the mouth have been linked to serious conditions like diabetes and high blood pressure. Dr. Nina Ricci Antipala-Rivera is dedicated to helping you maintain optimal oral health to keep you as healthy and happy as possible.</p>
                    <p>Our goal is to help our patients make informed choices about the level of dental health that is most appropriate for them. Instead of telling you how healthy you ought to be, we will be here to help you develop dental health choices and encourage you to make informed decisions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
